---
title: HelloHero: Teriyaki-Glazed Pork Burger with Creamy Slaw & Sesame-Bacon Fries
description: We're revamping burger night by giving juicy pork patties a teriyaki glaze, and sprinkling potato fries with sesame seeds and bacon to jazz up their flavour. A rainbow slaw with pear and mayo takes the salad portion of the meal to new heights too.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/6757a2b37668eda5b4113608-73eb94d2.jpeg
